KNN Regression (single predictor): Fit


\(K=1\)

knnfit1 &lt;- nearest_neighbor(neighbors = 1) |&gt; 
  set_engine("kknn") |&gt; 
  set_mode("regression") |&gt; 
  fit(profit ~ population, data = outlets)   # 1-nn regression
predict(knnfit1, new_data = tibble(population = 6)) |&gt; kable()  # 1-nn prediction




.pred




